structure.unit: PHYSICIANS, OSTEOPATHS, PODIATRISTS, AND RELATED MEDICAL PRACTITIONERS

law.text: KRS 311.550 to 311.620 may be cited as the "Kentucky Medical and Osteopathic Practice Act of 1972."
law.history: Amended 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 218, sec. 17. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 150, sec. 16, effective June 19, 1952.
